stories.text:
Things to look before starting to trade or mint NFTs

1. Have a Metamask or Trust wallet (Cold wallet), ( secretly store your seed phrase)

2. Transfer some crypto funds to your Cold wallet, (A small amount)

3. Check out https://rarity.tools/ for upcoming NFT projects,

4. Search for any of the NFT Marketplace, https://opensea.io/ (OpenSea) https://rarible.com/ (Rarible) https://www.airnfts.com/ https://lnkd.in/gDXg676P (Wazirx NFT Marketplace)

5. What are you now waiting for, go and start exploring, minting, collecting, and trading #NFTS.

Point to be noted, NFT Marketplace is a very illiquid market, it might take weeks, months, or maybe even years to sell your first #NFT, and neither of this is a piece of financial advice, it's only for educational purpose and do your proper research before investing.
